name: Tsunomaki Watame (5 Outfits) | Hololive
description:
Form for requests.

I also sometimes do polls on my Patreon for the next LoRA (no payment required).


I'm still not quite sure if version 4 is an upgrade or not. Let's call it a sidegrade for the time being. It seems to be more consistent with her outfits, while making her ears less fluffy :(
After some testing it seems that adding "poiny ears" to negative, and "sheep ears" to positive, can help bring back the fluff in some cases.

A weight of ~1.0 is recommended. You may need to adjust depending on your model.
Feel free to experiment with other weights and share your results if you want to!

The main prompt is "Tsunomaki Watame"
Sometimes adding "sheep girl, sheep ears, etc." can help with some models.

For her outfits try:

Normal Outfit:

Tsunomaki Watame, long hair, WatameBase, fur-trimmed dress, white dress, bare shoulders, fur-trimmed sleeves, hairclip, cape, belt pouch, brooch, fur-trimmed boots

Casual Outfit:

Tsunomaki Watame, side ponytail, WatameCasual, striped dress, sailor collar, hairclip, red choker, see-through sleeves, white bow, cardigan, open cardigan

Sleepwear:

Tsunomaki Watame, hair bun, WatameSleep, blue jacket, open jacket, camisole, hairclip, thigh strap, hair flower, short shorts, pink shorts, barefoot

Watame Night Fever:

Tsunomaki Watame, very long hair, WatameIdol, black dress, halterneck, detached sleeves, hairclip, red gloves, single glove, thigh strap, overskirt, hair ribbon, bare shoulders

New Year's:

Tsunomaki Watame, twin braids, long hair, WatameKimono, floral print, red kimono, sash, hair flower, bow, fur scarf, hat


Let me know if you have any issues.

Used embeddings for sample pictures:

EasyNegative

bad_prompt_version2

If you have any feedback or questions just write in the comments or hit me up on reddit or discord.

V3 Tags:
The main prompt is "Watame"

For her outfits try:

Normal Outfit:

Watame, long hair, WatameOutfit, bag, fur collar, fur-trimmed dress

Casual Outfit:

Watame, WatameCasual, short sleeves, short hair, side ponytail, ribbon choker

swap short sleeves with cardigan, if you want hear to wear it.

Sleepwear:

Watame, WatameSleep, jacket, pink shorts, short hair, hair bun

The dataset was quite limited for this one :(

New Year's Outfit:

Watame, WatameKimono, long hair, bangs, twin braids
